s3033: Eighteenth year: attacked Xu; the Xu ruler bared his torso in submission; Chu accepted it.
s3060: Twenty-fifth year: Xiang Wang established; feared Tai Shu.
s3063: Twenty-fifth year: attacked Di; because of Chong Er.
s3066: Thirtieth year: the duke was ill; Crown Prince Zi Fu yielded to his elder brother Mu Yi as worthy; the duke did not listen.
s3076: Xiang Wang's first year: the feudal lords established the king.
s3077: Ninth year: Qi led us to attack Jin's disorder, reached Gao Liang and returned.
s3078: Thirty-fifth year: in summer, assembled the feudal lords at Kui Qiu. The Son of Heaven sent Steward Kong to grant the sacrificial meat, commanded no bowing.
s3079: Twenty-sixth year: the duke died; established Xi Qi; Li Ke killed him. And Zhuo Zi. Established Yi Wu.
s3080: Ninth year: Yi Wu sent Xi Kui to bribe, seeking entry.
s3082: Thirty-first year: the duke passed away, not yet buried; Qi Huan assembled at Kui Qiu.
s3094: Thirty-sixth year: sent Xi Peng to establish Jin Hui Gong.
s3095: Jin Hui Gong Yi Wu's first year: executed Li Ke, violated the Qin alliance.
s3096: Tenth year: Pi Zheng Zi Bao fled and came.
s3098: Song Xiang Gong Zi Fu's first year: Mu Yi was chancellor.
s3108: Third year: the Rong attacked us; Tai Shu Dai summoned them. Wanted to execute Shu Dai; Shu Dai fled to Qi.
s3112: Eleventh year: rescued the king and attacked the Rong; the Rong left.
s3119: Twenty-fourth year: had a concubine who dreamed heaven gave her an orchid, gave birth to Mu Gong Lan.
s3126: Thirty-eighth year: had Guan Zhong pacify the Rong at Zhou, wished to receive upper minister rites, declined, accepted lower minister rites.
